node.text: Who wants to come ride for a day? I’ve accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE @AllInChallenge. I am partnering with my friends @Burton, @MammothMountain and @IkonPass. Go to https://allinchallenge.in/shaunwhite or click the link in my bio to enter. We are offering a chance to ride with yours truly, a three-day stay at the slope side Mammoth Mountain Inn, a complete Burton snowboard setup, and an Ikon pass for the 20/21 season. I’m so stoked to be doing this! Looking forward to seeing you on the mountain! I nominate @Zedd, @JoeJonas and @JulesHough to be all in!
